                <div >
                    <section class="section section-content">
                        <div>
                            <div class="column small-12 medium-12 large-12 large-centered text-center">
                                <div class="main" role="main" id="howto-section">
                                    <div id="content" >
                                        
                                        <h1  id="howto-title" itemprop='headline'>Where you can ride transit using Apple Pay</h1>
                                        <div class="intro"><p>Learn where you can ride transit using Apple Pay on your iPhone and Apple Watch.</p>

</div>
                                        

                                        <div itemprop='author' itemscope itemtype='http://schema.org/Organization'>
                                            <meta itemprop='name' content='Apple' />
                                        </div>

                                        <div id="sections" itemprop="articleBody">
                                            
    
        <div >
    

    
            
            <div  ><p>If your country or region isn't listed, check with your transit agency to see if they support payment using Apple Pay.</p>
<p>Depending on your location, you can&nbsp;<a href="https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT209494" aria-label="Add a transit card to Apple Wallet">add a transit card</a>&nbsp;or use the payment cards already in your Wallet app.</p>

</div>
            
        </div>

    
        <div >
    

    
            <h2>Asia-Pacific</h2>
            <div  ><p><strong>Australia</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Sydney: Transport for NSW. Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>China mainland</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Add a China T-Union transit card*. Ride anywhere this card is accepted.</li>
<li>Beijing: Add a Beijing Transit card*. Ride anywhere this card is accepted.</li>
<li>Shanghai: Add a Shanghai Transit card*. Ride anywhere this card is accepted.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Hong Kong</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong></strong>Add an Octopus card*. Ride anywhere this card is accepted.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Japan</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Add a Suica card* or a PASMO card*. Ride anywhere these cards are accepted.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Singapore</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Land Transport Authority (LTA). Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Taiwan</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kaohsiun and Taoyuan Airport MRT. Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app.</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="note">*<a href="https://support.apple.com/kb/HT212171" aria-label="Use Express Mode with transit cards">Express Mode</a> supported.</span></p>

</div>
            
        </div>

    
        <div >
    

    
            
            <div  ><p><img alt="" src="/library/content/dam/edam/applecare/images/en_US/mac_apps/itunes/divider.png"></p>

</div>
            
        </div>

    
        <div >
    

    
            <h2>Europe</h2>
            <div  ><p><strong>Belarus</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Minsk: Minsk Metro. Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app*.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Finland</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Turku: Föli. Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app*.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Russia</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Multiple cities accept payment cards in the Wallet app.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Sweden</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Skåne: Skånetrafiken city buses. Accepts payment cards in Wallet app*.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>United Kingdom</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Arriva UK Bus. Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app.*</li>
<li>Brighton & Hove Buses. Accepts payment cards in Wallet app*.</li>
<li>First Bus Group.&nbsp;Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app*.</li>
<li>London: Transport for London (TfL). Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app*.</li>
<li>Metrobus. Accepts payment cards in Wallet app*.</li>
<li>Oxford Bus Company. Accepts payment cards in Wallet app*.</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="note">*<a href="https://support.apple.com/kb/HT212171" aria-label="Use Express Mode with transit cards">Express Mode</a> supported.</span></p>

</div>
            
        </div>

    
        <div >
    

    
            
            <div  ><p><img alt="" src="/library/content/dam/edam/applecare/images/en_US/mac_apps/itunes/divider.png"></p>

</div>
            
        </div>

    
        <div >
    

    
            <h2>North America</h2>
            <div  ><p><strong>Canada</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Vancouver: TransLink. Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>United States</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Chicago: Add a Ventra card*. Ride anywhere this card is accepted or pay with payment cards in the Wallet app.</li>
<li>Los Angeles: Add a TAP card*. Ride anywhere these cards are accepted.</li>
<li>New York City: Metropolitan Transportation Authority (MTA). Accepts payment cards in the Wallet app*.</li>
<li>Portland: Add a Hop Fastpass*. Ride anywhere this card is accepted or pay with payment cards in the Wallet app.</li>
<li>San Francisco Bay Area: Add a Clipper card*. Ride anywhere this card is accepted.</li>
<li>Washington, D.C.: Add a SmarTrip card*. Ride anywhere this card&nbsp;is accepted.</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="note">*<a href="https://support.apple.com/kb/HT212171" aria-label="Use Express Mode with transit cards">Express Mode</a> supported.</span></p>

</div>
            
        </div>


                                        </div>
                                        
                                        
